text: Prajakta Koli known for her YouTube Channel MostlySane, is an Indian YouTuber and actress who makes comedy videos. She is also known for her lead role in the Netflix romantic drama Mismatched. == Early and personal life == Koli was born and brought up in Thane. She studied in Vasant Vihar High School in Thane. She graduated with a Bachelor of Mass Media from V. G. Vaze College of Arts, Science and Commerce in Mulund, affiliated to the University of Mumbai. Prajakta Koli is in a relationship with Vrishank Khanal, who is a lawyer by profession. ==References== Category:Indian people Category:YouTubers Category:1993 births Category:Living people
